Reliance Capital Gets RBI Approval for Unit Stake Sale

-- B y   N i v e d i t h a   R a v i
-- 
2011-09-30T04:58:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-30/reliance-capital-gets-rbi-approval-for-unit-stake-sale.html
Reliance Capital Ltd. (RCAPT)  received
approval from  India ’s central bank for a proposed stake sale in
its life insurance unit to  Japan ’s Nippon Life Insurance Co.,
according to a stock exchange filing today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
